And, here they use
different luminance levels.

00:04:13.410 --> 00:04:15.550
So they make it brighter and,
or brighter and,

00:04:15.550 --> 00:04:17.779
it's sort of how sensitive you are.

00:04:17.779 --> 00:04:22.450
And then something, and for the PETA
folks amongst you, please ignore this.

00:04:22.450 --> 00:04:25.100
You'll notice that the human data and

00:04:25.100 --> 00:04:28.950
the macaque, macaque is a type of
monkey, are very, very similar.

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:33.200
Now, this is done, of course, without
doing anything to anybody, right?

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:34.850
You just ask them what do you see,
et cetera.

00:04:35.850 --> 00:04:39.970
But what this data show is that the
vision system, the retinal vision system

00:04:39.970 --> 00:04:43.920
