quite similar to the human.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:48.390
So if you were to do experiments on
primates measuring physiological things,

00:04:48.390 --> 00:04:51.400
remember those electrodes,
we have reason to believe that what

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:55.440
we learn there is the same,
would apply also to the human system.

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:57.790
So, when you have psychophysical
experiments like this,

00:04:57.790 --> 00:05:01.180
